4 forks with a few adds based on other reviews... - I toasted the pine nuts and added them at the very end - Add 1/2 c white wine and 1/4 c lemon juice after the garlic. Let it cook down a bit and then proceed. - Almost forgot! Added a little crushed red pepper. - This was so, so, so good! I will make again and again. Would be great with chicken or shrimp added.

